not been clearedcitation needed Mixtapes can also take other artists beats and simply add new verses top generally labelled remix freestyle Albums the other hand only contain samples that have been cleared order avoid legal issues Albums are also almost always sold whereas mixtapes are usually free The modern form mixtape that made popular following Cent and his group GUnit the early 2000s sometimes containing all original music other times composed freestyles and remixes popular tracks There are exceptions such the Free Weezy Album Lil Wayne which the name suggests was free album Another Youre Reading This Its Too Late mixtape Drake sold for profit 